# PhonicsForge requires NO environment variables, secrets, or accounts.
#
# The entire app runs client-side in the browser:
#   - Speech analysis (DSP) runs on-device via the Web Audio API
#   - Game state persists locally (localStorage)
#   - No backend, no API keys, no telemetry
#
# This file exists only to document that fact. There is nothing to fill in.
#
# Optional, for the *production* roadmap (NOT needed to run the MVP):
# VITE_ASR_ENDPOINT=   # URL of a self-hosted wav2vec2 phoneme-scoring service
